NAME

IPC::Signal::Force - force default handling of a signal

DESCRIPTION

This module exports one function, "force_raise", which invokes a default
signal handler regardless of the signal's current handling.

INSTALLATION

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

